<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; padding: 24px; background-color: #f8fafc;">
    <div style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border: 1px border #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
        <h2 style="color: #4f46e5; margin-top: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800;">Planora.</h2>
        <h3 style="color: #1e293b; margin-top: 24px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;">Reset Your Password</h3>
        <p style="color: #475569; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px;">Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p style="color: #475569; font-size: 14px; leading-height: 1.5;">We received a request to reset your password for your Planora account. Click the button below to configure a new password. This link is only valid for 15 minutes:</p>
        <div style="margin: 28px 0; text-align: center;">
            <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 12px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2);">
                Reset Password
            </a>
        </div>
        <p style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 32px; border-t: 1px border #f1f5f9; pt: 16px;">If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your current password remains active.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
